## What's Changed
* Update Configuration.swift `handleOpenURL` and `authorize` to support async await    
  @LucasCoderT #192
* add some more fields to repo, and structure for organization    
   @armcknight #191
* Use Xcode 16 and swift 5.10    
   @pietbrauer #196
* feat: add repo topics    
   @armcknight #197
* Extend the Pull Request API    
   @4np #195

## New Contributors
* @armcknight made their first contribution in https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/191
* @4np made their first contribution in https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/195

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/compare/0.13.0...0.14.0

## What's Changed
* async/await functions for Star/unstar   
   @417-72KI https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/151
* Allow for authorization header to be set   
   @clayellis https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/154
* Add patch pull request   
   @tboogh https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/156
* Add devcontainer config   
   @pietbrauer https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/157
* Sort keys in JSON Fixtures   
   @pietbrauer https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/158
* Add Latest Release Endpoint   
   @brianmichel https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/164
* Fix LableRouter Paths   
   @cwagdev https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/165
* New endpoint: `Create a review for a pull request`   
   @417-72KI https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/169
* Add Swiftformat SPM Plugin   
   @pietbrauer https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/170
* OctoKitCLI   
   @pietbrauer https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/159
* Adding ability to create new pull request.   
   @ps2 https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/167
* Move URLSession to Octokit instead of having it in every method   
   @pietbrauer https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/160
* Add init for SwiftUI Preview   
   @zunda-pixel https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/172
* Add `List pull requests files` endpoint   
   @417-72KI https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/173
* fix: add missing documentation for `generateNotes` param of `postRelease`   
   @b-onc https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/174
* Update SwiftFormat Plugin   
   @pietbrauer https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/177
* Add pagination to PullRequests   
   @sfaxon https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/176
* Run CI on main   
   @pietbrauer https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/178
* Add pagination for Statuses   
   @sfaxon https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/179
* add missing ci_activity to notification reasons   
   @amcleodca https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/180
* Add search code endpoint   
   @chidiwilliams https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/182
* dateDecodingStrategy added as described in Issue #184   
   @gregorFeigel https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/185
* Update Xcode to 15.4   
   @pietbrauer https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/187
* Milestone api   
   @leszko11 https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/186
* Fix and add some endpoints for `review`   
   @417-72KI https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/171
* Implement Repository contents API   
   @Nikoloutsos https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/189
* Async notifications support + added endpoints   
   @LucasCoderT https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/pull/183

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/nerdishbynature/octokit.swift/compare/0.12.0...0.13.0

- Allow GitHub API calls to be discarded #70   
  @orta 
