   @stephenyao 
- Bump Xcode, RequestKit and Swift versions #76    
   @rubiojr 
- Resolved problems when posting Issues #77    
   @vincode-io 
- Added support for Gists #78.  
   @vincode-io 
- Add methods to get and create labels #80    
   @robmathers 
